member.param:
vui label, so that qualification parsing can use field display labels
            per the given vui. 
            null - no display labels be considered; 
            "" - field display label per the default vui; 
            "SomeVuiLabelHere" - the field display labels per this vui 
            Field database ids can always be used in qualifications.

